Package: promethiumR
Type: Package
Title: Advanced Seismic Data Recovery and Reconstruction Framework
Version: 1.0.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Promethium", "Contributors", email = "promethium@example.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Native R implementation of the Promethium framework for seismic 
    data recovery and reconstruction. Provides algorithms for missing trace 
    interpolation, denoising, and signal reconstruction using classical signal 
    processing (Wiener filtering, bandpass filters), optimization-based methods 
    (matrix completion via ISTA, compressive sensing via FISTA), and deep 
    learning (U-Net, autoencoders). Part of the multi-language Promethium 
    ecosystem with mathematically consistent implementations in Python, Julia, 
    and Scala.
License: CC BY-NC 4.0
URL: https://github.com/olaflaitinen/Promethium
BugReports: https://github.com/olaflaitinen/Promethium/issues
